What's the mood in Gibraltar ahead of the EU referendum?

2016-06-16

We’d like to know how those living in Gibraltar feel about the EU referendum. Are you concerned about a possible Brexit or do you feel that many will be voting to remain in the EU?

Share your photos and views by clicking on the blue ‘Contribute’ button on this article. You can also use the Guardian app and search for ‘GuardianWitness assignments’ – and if you add it to the homepage – you can keep up with all our assignments. Alternatively you can fill in our form below.

We’ll include a selection of your contributions in our ongoing reporting on the referendum.

